-- MOVES-U.S. Bancorp hires John Briggs as consultant
-- 
-- Tue Dec 09, 2014 03:05PM EST
-- None



Dec 9 (Reuters) - U.S. Bancorp <USB.N> hired John Briggs as a wealth management consultant and an entertainment industry specialist to its Private Client Reserve business.

Briggs will be responsible in developing relationships with clients in the entertainment industry.  He will also assemble a team of wealth management professionals to provide customized solutions, the company said.